      <odd id="aspace_5efb7b47ba2eda376d619ff71e7875e1">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 37 (YRG 37), Records of associations, institutes, centers, and organizations affiliated with Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_a79d2307e74bde2aacafeba966fb022e">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Human Relations Area Files Records (RU 476). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a4b3d2e454a41cd0817582e5b5d31fdf">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_8b5033f36a8dc21cb00e7c79c3463724">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Human Relations Area Files (HRAF) was founded at Yale University in 1949. Its mission is to "encourage and facilitate worldwide comparative studies of human behavior, society, and culture."</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_2eb4ccc8ff18673bb9ee11f633eabeba">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of minutes, correspondence, memoranda, bibliographies, reports, and papers documenting the activities and operations of the Human Relations Area Files.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
